This paper deals with pilot reuse in multi-cell massive MIMO systems, which is a topic related to information theory (cs.IT), network infrastructure (cs.NI), and system and control theory (cs.SY). The paper also discusses the optimization of the weighted sum rate, which is a topic related to machine learning (cs.LG) and multimedia systems (cs.MM). Therefore, these five categories are the most likely ones for this paper.
